{
  "id": "RAW_d52eaf",
  "title": "即梦图片 3.0 又重磅更新，这可能是对普通人最有用的一次。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/o_G7ZUKsf7CoYnJeMZLriQ",
  "date": "2025-06-06 00:00:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨天晚上，即梦的最强AI绘图模型图片3.0，又又又更新了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">内测上线了即梦图片3.0的，智能参考，现在，可以垫图了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7314814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188017\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1fa7078c-a89f-4cfa-3f40-2759d3f4a700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1fa7078c-a89f-4cfa-3f40-2759d3f4a700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">MD，这次连设计师的参考图也一键干碎了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我测了整整一夜，现在是凌晨4点21，我还在写这篇文章。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我人真的傻了，我真的不愿意用一些什么很夸张的词语，但是即梦的绘图，每一次，带给我的震撼，都会觉得，我这么多年的设计师生涯，在AI的进化速度面前，不值一提。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">什么样的言语，都无法比拟直接看图来的直接，直接给你们看效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是一张，很好看的北京的字体设计。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3342592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188015\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0451aff3-ef2b-4679-ad37-76ac84847200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0451aff3-ef2b-4679-ad37-76ac84847200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而现在，我很喜欢这个字体设计，我想把北京，变成上海。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你只需要把这张图传给即梦，说，变成上海。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188016\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f870a97a-c46d-4364-ec62-d2aa4a2e0800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f870a97a-c46d-4364-ec62-d2aa4a2e0800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，就一句话，太离谱了，真的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我一定要给你们看看细节，北京的字体设计里面，是有天坛地标的，而上海的设计里面，他自己把地标东方明珠也加上了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188018\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da756d3c-c8ac-4f8c-48ef-b6533718b900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da756d3c-c8ac-4f8c-48ef-b6533718b900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">做过设计的人都知道，做这种字体，有多复杂，但是现在，你只要一个效果，一键。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有可以，继续一句话，做成杭州、新疆、成都。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188019\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f7c9bec-14fd-46e0-1e2f-b43c0ceb8e00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f7c9bec-14fd-46e0-1e2f-b43c0ceb8e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Prompt：把文字改成“宇宙电波”</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188020\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3a67f5fd-8e5d-4f49-8710-141644556200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3a67f5fd-8e5d-4f49-8710-141644556200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有朋友@倒放</span><span leaf=\"\">做的，把“九”，改成“十”。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188051\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e65613c8-aff4-49c0-85da-40b0e5613900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e65613c8-aff4-49c0-85da-40b0e5613900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一键改表情包的字，什么叫表情包自由，这就是。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188024\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57c8498b-b4a1-4388-2289-471eb150cf00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57c8498b-b4a1-4388-2289-471eb150cf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5138888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188025\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d3381776-105f-4dd1-5f98-6ccf51dc4c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d3381776-105f-4dd1-5f98-6ccf51dc4c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">打麻将打的不爽了？把发发发换成胡胡胡。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188029\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/99b89056-1d76-4f7d-0b74-c59b2b9b6500/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/99b89056-1d76-4f7d-0b74-c59b2b9b6500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">@阿真Irene</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直接随手拍了一下面包，一键做成产品海报</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188028\" data-ratio=\"0.9296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/faa8743f-a31c-4feb-fd34-0eba6a018300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/faa8743f-a31c-4feb-fd34-0eba6a018300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有各种电商海报。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一杯奶茶。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188054\" data-ratio=\"0.6976744186046512\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1032\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba1ae733-08bb-4636-091f-8546bfc4b800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ba1ae733-08bb-4636-091f-8546bfc4b800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一键直出4种海报风格。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188052\" data-ratio=\"0.4388888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8649d4f6-4742-4f33-da2b-914ca8dae700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8649d4f6-4742-4f33-da2b-914ca8dae700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">太牛逼了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我2015年入行，从事UI设计，然后中途干过交互，干过视觉，干过用研究，后面带团队当设计总监。现在也10年了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这10年，见证了风格从拟物走向扁平，从2.5D走向轻拟物，从C4D到新拟态，各种风格流转，但是我想，2015年我第一次坐在公司里，画那4个状态页插画的时候，绝对想象不到，10年后的今天，是TM这么做设计的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前写过即梦的3.0绘图模型，中文字直出这方面可以说是孤独求败，补齐AI生图的最大短板。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是当时的3.0还是有一些遗憾的，很多朋友留言无法垫图。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188034\" data-ratio=\"0.3509259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02c53495-7326-4204-5475-edad4a2a7c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02c53495-7326-4204-5475-edad4a2a7c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以现在，即梦图片3.0的智能参考，它来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给大家看看什么叫做智能参考，怎么用。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"304\" data-imgfileid=\"500188031\" data-ratio=\"0.2175925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1396\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75f1d88f-a6f2-4948-2240-e93c3a037c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75f1d88f-a6f2-4948-2240-e93c3a037c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点这个框就能上传图片，上传图片后，你会看到一堆选项。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188032\" data-ratio=\"0.9203703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c52cafc6-742c-411c-745c-5b906cf15100/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c52cafc6-742c-411c-745c-5b906cf15100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">什么都不用管，就选这个智能参考，别管别的，就选它。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188078\" data-ratio=\"0.46296296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/009707db-7f9c-41ef-8f9e-ff7a1f4bf300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/009707db-7f9c-41ef-8f9e-ff7a1f4bf300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后选择图片3.0就行了，这，就是图片3.0的智能参考功能，对字体的设计，简直断档的无敌。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过这次即梦应该也是灰度内测，群里很多很多人都没有，如果你选完了以后，发现没有3.0，只能用图片2.0 Pro，那就说明没有被灰度到。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">具体全量上线时间，我也不知道，但是按照即梦过去几次的节奏，应该也就一两周的时间。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当你把图片上传上去以后，直接写你的Prompt就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如说我们现在要给做一个海报，以@阿真Irene给我发的这个包为例，我太喜欢这个包了，炒鸡可爱。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500188056\" data-ratio=\"0.6898148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4b1d5b24-e60e-418a-622f-e738c6678e00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4b1d5b24-e60e-418a-622f-e738c6678e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我脑子里看到他想到的第一个标题，就是“别惹我，我是鸡”，副标题是：“今天我不做人了”。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">于是，我就把这个包传到了即梦上，然后写了这么一段Prompt：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">设计一张情绪类潮玩单品海报，背景为</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">红橙撞黄</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">背景，整体风格偏爆款感。主体为一只愤怒表情的鸡造型毛绒包，形象居中稍偏下，底部搭配拟人化道具或地面（如草地、红毯、战斗擂台）。画面上方用无衬线字体写出主标题：“别惹我，我是鸡”，字体有立体描边，风格夸张、有表情装饰。副标题：“今天我不做人了”采用无衬线标签风文字，放于右上角或左下角。四周加入毛绒元素、搞笑情绪贴纸、emoji表情、拟人动作特效等图层点缀。整体风格强调爆款感、记忆点强、有梗有情绪，适用于玩具类、毛绒周边、社交图传播海报。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">得到的效果，是这样的。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188058\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/471d0bfc-1800-4bcd-8ab5-808453351a00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/471d0bfc-1800-4bcd-8ab5-808453351a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而非常坦诚的讲，为了得到这两张我觉得还不错的图，我roll了3轮，也就是12次，并不是因为有BUG，即梦图片3.0在写中文字上几乎已经到了登峰造极的水准了，文字几乎没有错，纯粹是，排版的审美上，你想要还不错的，那还是需要roll一roll的。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188059\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e58f209e-7f4b-4fb4-4cf8-aff8fd837c00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e58f209e-7f4b-4fb4-4cf8-aff8fd837c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过还在即梦的积分是真的太太太便宜了，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">生成4张图只要2积分，要知道，每天即梦还送66积分呢。。。无敌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们还可以，给包换个风格，换个软萌软萌的可爱风格，也没有任何问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Prompt：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">构建一张可爱反差萌风格的海报，背景为奶油粉渐变，搭配糖果、云朵、小兔贴纸等元素。鸡包垫图居中，周围环绕“表情贴纸”“表情气泡”“炸毛感小情绪”。主标题用手写体或奶油厚字写出“软萌也能暴走”，副标题为“小女生也有大脾气”。整体风格偏日系反差感。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188060\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8daa6dd7-f4c4-4af4-f2b3-fdf1e435e900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8daa6dd7-f4c4-4af4-f2b3-fdf1e435e900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">即梦图片3.0本身，我自己感觉，也比之前的有了更新，对Prompt更精准更可控，也更敏感了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你想生成一张不错的海报，那还是需要写的比较详细，好好Roll一Roll的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这块，我建议善用AI，比如DeepSeek、GPT啥的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再看看其他的，即梦图片3.0和智能参考生成的海报。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5833333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188068\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a9525214-5481-4563-9601-bc4c7c674200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a9525214-5481-4563-9601-bc4c7c674200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8722222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188069\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ae10dd7c-d7de-467a-0ee5-1cbbe4382200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ae10dd7c-d7de-467a-0ee5-1cbbe4382200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188065\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0fff1dce-5780-4c73-04b0-b50cc99ddd00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0fff1dce-5780-4c73-04b0-b50cc99ddd00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过这里有一个小点需要注意，就是你给的产品图片，如果是透明底的PNG图片，抠干净的，效果会非常好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是，但是，一定要注意一下，不要是webp格式的，这个格式巨坑，网上现在有时候下图会下到webp格式的透明底的图，这种图扔到即梦图片3.0里面生成，必出锯齿，非常的离谱。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48055555555555557\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188077\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bdcbeaab-7636-4790-adaa-0eb6ad4d5b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bdcbeaab-7636-4790-adaa-0eb6ad4d5b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了把产品做成海报之外，你也可以做可爱的萌宠图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Prompt：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">图片顶部文字“撸猫图解”，头部和脖子区域，搭配文字“爽”，腹部区域，搭配文字“请你走开”，后腿区域，搭配“高危区”</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4981481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188066\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e0d8980f-e92e-44b4-cc5a-411ac75a2900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e0d8980f-e92e-44b4-cc5a-411ac75a2900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从这个case，你就应该能看出来，即梦图片3.0这近乎变态的精准控制了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不止宠物，又或者，给你的小美女，加一个可爱的边框。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7379629629629629\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188044\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b5c749e1-573b-4225-87fa-fc5b17fab300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b5c749e1-573b-4225-87fa-fc5b17fab300/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或者，画一些抽象的小漫画。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188070\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3232b9fd-2a70-47cf-1667-c20d14095200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3232b9fd-2a70-47cf-1667-c20d14095200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有一个让我笑不拢嘴的表情包case。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188071\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5815147d-2fdc-4124-8944-eb053f120400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5815147d-2fdc-4124-8944-eb053f120400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我真的，看一次笑一次。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">至于改字就更简单了，直接用嘴说就行，就跟最开始case一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5953703703703703\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188048\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bc9a5720-6674-49af-47e7-a1c366aa1a00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bc9a5720-6674-49af-47e7-a1c366aa1a00/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有好朋友@倒放做的这个炒鸡恶搞的例子，把母猪产后护理难，问XXXX，直接改成了，P图不用动，直接用即梦，我看到真的笑抽了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6027777777777777\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 562px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/OjgKEXmLURrWl6yvvKlsDbsztOsHttPjCmtsX1ib6drUH3YSuj5pAUf44GQxVn1aCRMdV0IoJ9ib7y8Qnp4WBHPA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"2719\" data-cropy2=\"1640.1085409252669\" data-imgfileid=\"500188072\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da4dad1f-8e12-4f3b-18a5-00d33881f400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da4dad1f-8e12-4f3b-18a5-00d33881f400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过在我的测试下，如果是一些超级复杂的或者设计感极强的字体，成功率还是会偏低的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如这个，目前还没有成功过，太复杂了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.27870370370370373\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188074\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3c9d9191-b5a6-4730-992e-2c55e6a1a800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3c9d9191-b5a6-4730-992e-2c55e6a1a800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不只是加字改字，换风格再加字，也是手到擒来了，比如@赛博小熊猫loki的这个case。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43333333333333335\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188047\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd545952-6752-46a4-d03a-fb603bbf3600/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd545952-6752-46a4-d03a-fb603bbf3600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看完上面这些案例，可以来总结一下了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">即梦把智能参考功能放到了中文字生成能力最强的3.0模型中，让即梦图片3.0在中文设计界成了真正的全能选手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以说，即梦图片3.0能覆盖90%以上的中文出图场景，从商品图、宣传海报、电影海报、专辑封面，到p照片、做表情包，它都能轻松实现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除此之外，不需要太怎么氪金就能体验，生成4张图只要2积分，普通用户甚至不需要氪金，靠每日领取积分就够了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.20277777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188035\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/509e3eb0-bcbf-45fd-2f48-46908155cc00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/509e3eb0-bcbf-45fd-2f48-46908155cc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而在中文理解和生成方面，即梦是当之无愧的第一名。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不需要科学上网，不需要英文交流，只要你脑子里有灵感，直接掏出来，用大白话告诉它就行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说实话，中文场景出图，还是得中国团队来做。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">写到最后，我在上海的酒店里，长叹了一口气。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">数学、代码等等进化，有时候我又一些钝感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为我不是那个行业的人，我有时候，无法理解，那种进化，对行业的冲击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是设计，是我干了，将近10年的行业。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是我从毕业到自媒体之前，赖以生存的玩意。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我太太能感受到，那种冲击了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，我还是想说说，设计师这个职业。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我想说，每次新出了什么好用的设计工具，很多人都在说“设计师的天塌了”、“RIP设计师”，我真的，无意、也不是很想，推崇这样的叙事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI技术力和审美都在以月、以天为单位，飞速发展，这已经成为常态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多人也在逐渐适应这种模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">训练AI做出不同的风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用不同的AI风格去匹配甲方的需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">摒弃重复繁琐的修改过程让AI一键实现需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多人享受到了AI的便利，省下了时间，提高了效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但同时，也像钝刀子割肉一样，AI越便利，越是一点点挤占自己的生存空间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但我们要做的，不是站在原地焦虑，而是不断地去连接一切人、事、物和体验，通过连接不断创新。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从人的角度去抓住最本质的用户心理，解决真正的痛点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像原研哉说的那样：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">生活是设计的起源地，而设计归根结底是对我们生活的发言。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI是一片肥沃的土壤，而你的生命体验，你的价值观，你的想法和创意才是最根本的根系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当一个nb的你，遇上一个nb的AI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也许，这就是属于你的黄金时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是最好的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也是最坏的时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">共勉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克、水衫</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http:/